data.description: MASSIVE BACK YARD, SWIMMING POOL, HOT TUB, NO REAR NEIGHBORS, NO HOA, GREAT WINTER PARK SCHOOLS, FIREPLACE, TONS KITCHEN STORAGE. One of the Largest Lots in the Bel Aire Pines Community with a Massive Yard in Winter Park with a Gorgeous Black Bottom Pool and Hot tub. Tons of extra space .  Lots of Yard Privacy with Orange County Conservation Canal behind the property. Tons of Kitchen Cabinets and Countertop space. Granite Countertops. Stainless Refrigerator, Dishwasher. Gorgeous Fireplace with built in storage and shelving located in one of the spaces as part of a Living, Family, and Dining Combo.  Two Car Garage. Large Covered and Screened Back Patio. Long Covered and Screened Patio extends the front of the home. Long Driveway with lots of parking.  Also large parking pad on the left side of the home perfect for Boat, RV or additional Car parking. LOCATED IN THE HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER "A" RANKED WINTER PARK HIGH SCHOOL which is also in the TOP 3 PUBLIC HIGH SCHOOLS IN ORANGE COUNTY with IB PROGRAM and AMONG THE TOP HIGH SCHOOLS in the STATE of FLORIDA. Home needs a few updates, but it has been priced accordingly.
